text: Kazi Abul Kashem is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Patuakhali-4. ==Career== Kashem was elected to parliament from Patuakhali-4 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. Kazi Abul Kashem Stadium was named after him. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
